---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£5Ô∏è‚É£ SECURITY & GOVERNANCE CONTROLS

* No manual override of publish time without audit log
* Two-factor authentication before high-value publication
* IP logging of publisher
* Automatic freeze if legal injunction issued
* System-wide suspension capability

---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£6Ô∏è‚É£ EDGE CASE HANDLING

* Emergency procurement (shortened timeline with justification log)
* Tender cancellation (must record reason)
* Tender extension (automatic notifications)
* Partial cancellation of lots
* Re-publication after cancellation
* Cross-border tenders

All must maintain transparency history.

---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£7Ô∏è‚É£ KPIs TO TRACK

* Supplier reach per tender
* Average number of bids per tender
* Time-to-bid ratio
* Amendment frequency
* Clarification response time
* SME participation rate
* Market concentration index

